item.title: Ieeja All-Party Committee Celebrates the Victory of Gadwal Bar Association
item.description: <![CDATA[Jogulamba Gadwal District, Ieeja Municipality Center: In a major development, the Gadwal Bar Association successfully secured the construction of a new court building at the BJP camp office, addressing public needs. This was achieved after days of protests and a hunger strike organized by the Bar Association in front of the Gadwal Court. The Ieeja All-Party Committee extended their full support to the Bar Association by joining the protest and uniting all political parties, public organizations,...]]>
item.author: M Veeresh
